author: HBO Max
description:
In Episode 6 of the Peacemaker Podcast, James Gunn, Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt), and Steve Agee (John Economos), with Chukwudi Iwuji (Clemson Murn) dive into behind-the-scenes stories from Season 1, Episode 6, “Murn After Reading” of the hit HBO Max series “Peacemaker,” with exclusive insights from Iwuji, who plays the enigmatic Clemson Murn. James Gunn leads the conversation, exploring the creative process, character development, and the unique chemistry among the cast. Listeners get a front-row seat to candid anecdotes, on-set challenges, and the evolution of Murn’s character arc. Jennifer, Steve, and Chukwudi share their perspectives on working with Gunn, the show’s impact on the DC Universe, and what fans can expect in future episodes. Subscribe for more easter eggs and behind-the-scenes breakdowns. New episodes drop Mondays and Thursdays. Stream Peacemaker on HBO Max.
